headline: Hewlett Packard Enterprise (HPE) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of enterprise technology company Hewlett Packard Enterprise (NYSE:HPE) jumped 2.2% in the afternoon session after Citigroup reiterated its Buy rating on the stock and raised its price target to $28 from $26.
